         They are actually called Haunted Seachests. I can't recall if I tried any undead spells on them. I read that there are five of them in the zone, but I usually just did the one offshore from the otter camps.</P><P>By the way, if you are fearing them underwater, watch where you are going with them. Ending up in the midst of several sirens is only entertaining for a short period of time. Trust me on this.</P><P>Umbrax of Rallos Zak<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
